Strong storms have been wreaking havoc as they barreled across North Carolina this weekend – and one scared witness caught some of the mayhem on camera.

Ed Braz, of Brier Creek, took video of an entire section of a condominium complex collapsing during the violent storm.

He was talking about how scary the storm was while taking the video in the town near Raleigh when the building came down into his back yard.

